title: Lee Sin Montage #14 ''BORN TO INSEC''

embed.description: Hey guys it's my 14th Lee Sin Montage feat. ArchSin ''BORN TO INSEC'' I will do more features in the future to help other great player with low subs to grow up! :) Hope u all enjoy, and if u did then please like, share & subscribe it help me out alot.

body:
Jo Leute hier mal wieder eine neue Lee Sin Montage von mir mit einem guten Freund aus Tunesien
